  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested a comparative analysis of international health insurance options (ASN, Bupa, Cigna) for a specific profile: 53-year-old Italian woman residing in France/Switzerland, focusing on alternative medicine coverage and avoiding medical examinations. Manus provided comprehensive analysis and then created and deployed a professional website presenting the comparative findings.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nPersonal insurance research for specific demographic and geographic requirements, with emphasis on alternative medicine coverage and medical examination avoidance strategies.\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nConducted detailed comparative analysis of three international health insurers, evaluating coverage options, pricing estimates, and entry requirements. Subsequently developed and deployed a professional responsive website to present the analysis.\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [report] Insurance Comparative Analysis — Detailed comparison of ASN International, Bupa Global, and Cigna Global for specified profile\n- [web_application] Insurance Comparison Website — Professional responsive website with tabbed navigation, comparative tables, and actionable recommendations\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Cigna Global identified as best for alternative medicine coverage\n- ASN International recommended as broker solution for avoiding medical exams\n- Bupa Global deemed less suitable for alternative medicine needs\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Rapid pivot from analysis to web deployment\n- Clear comparative framework with actionable recommendations\n- Professional UI design with intuitive navigation\nDiscoveries:\n\n- ASN International operates as broker rather than direct insurer\n- Moratoire subscription type can help avoid medical examinations\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Contact ASN International for targeted brokerage search\n- Request detailed quote from Cigna Global\n- Publish website for permanent access\n---\nUID: nKzZxfKPnx3UdcU86gwPxC | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0128\n"
}